### **4. 24_ChartFlowPanel**  
**Description:**  
Renders a real-time, scrollable chart for visualizing incoming numerical streams.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# ChartFlowPanel - Realtime Numeric Stream Visualizer

ChartFlowPanel makes it easy to turn metrics or simulation output into live-updating, clean visual graphs.

## Features
- Smooth line scrolling  
- Adjustable update rate  
- Minimalist design  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/24_ChartFlowPanel.git
cd 24_ChartFlowPanel
python visualize.py
